display="inline"><![CDATA[K]]></fr:tex> on the right such that
    <fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[       \operatorname {H}^r(X_q,K^{p,q})       =0       \quad \text {for } p,q\geqslant 0 \text { and } r>0.     ]]></fr:tex>
    If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[K]]></fr:tex> is such a resolution, then we canonically have that

