display="inline"><![CDATA[K]]></fr:tex>;
    for what follows, we are free to <fr:em>define</fr:em> <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {H}^\bullet (X_\bullet ,F^\bullet )]]></fr:tex> by <fr:ref
addr="hodge-theory-iii-5.2.3.1"
href="hodge-theory-iii-5.2.3.1.xml"
taxon="Equation"
number="5.2.3.1" />.
    We can further show that the spectral sequence of the complex <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathrm {s}\Gamma ^\bullet (X_\bullet ,K)]]></fr:tex>, filtered by <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L]]></fr:tex> (<fr:ref
addr="hodge-theory-iii-5.1.9.3"
href="hodge-theory-iii-5.1.9.3.xml"
